race.comment: IN THE STARS (6) was rewarded with her maiden success last start, scoring by 7 lengths over 1609m at Kentucky (Turf). Looks well placed and she is a leading contender. MODERN SOUND (12) turned in a much better effort last start when beaten only 0.1 lengths into second at Kentucky (Turf) over 1408m. Sure to go well again. CLIFFS (14) was prominent at the turn and finished second last time over 1811m at Saratoga (Turf), beaten 0.8 lengths. In the right race and is a key runner. CAITLIN TIME (16) was in contention on the bend and finished third last start at the first run back from a spell over 1408m at Kentucky (Turf), beaten 0.6 lengths. Will strip fitter this time. Should be about the money. Something for the Multiples: WHIPPOORWILL (7) MY SEXY BLONDE (4)
